      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "ℹ️ S-14 LUT Export — round-trip color-grade into portable .cube\n\nChain: N-12 HALD Identity (level=8, 512×512) → N-09 Tone Curve (s_curve_mild) → N-13 LUT Export (.cube).\n\nN-12 generates an identity HALD image encoding a 64×64×64 color cube. Everything you wire between N-12 and N-13 gets *baked into* the exported LUT — any chain that is color-grade-only (Tone Curve, Color Matcher, Luminosity Masking blends, etc.) becomes a portable .cube you can load into DaVinci Resolve / Premiere / OBS / OCIO / hardware LUT boxes.\n\nN-13's `level` pin MUST match the level from N-12 (wired here via the INT link). The `filename` defaults to 'pack_lut.cube' under ComfyUI's output/ directory; absolute paths are honored verbatim. The '.cube' extension is auto-appended if you leave it off.\n\nDO NOT wire anything pixel-structure-aware (sharpening, denoise, detail masks, face pipeline, skin smoother, lens distortion) between N-12 and N-13 — those operators are spatial, not color-only, and will NOT linearize into a 3D LUT."
      ],
